OL,3,CThe King and Queen visit 9/11 memorial
OL,4,Cas part of US state visit
OL,6,FThe King and Queen have arrived at the
OL,7,F9/11 Memorial in New York on the third
OL,8,Fday of their state visit to the United
OL,9,FStates, as ITV News Royal Editor Chris
OL,10,FShip reports
OL,12,FKing Charles III and Queen Camilla
OL,13,Fbegan their trip to New York City on
OL,14,FWednesday with a visit to the National
OL,15,F9/11 Memorial, as the 25th anniversary
OL,16,Fof the attacks approaches.
OL,18,FThe stop is part of the royal couple's
OL,19,Ffour-day US state visit, marking 250
OL,20,Fyears of American independence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
