PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777529104
OL,3,CThe King and Queen visit 9/11 memorial
OL,4,Cas part of US state visit
OL,6,FThe royal couple honoured victims of
OL,7,Fthe 11 September attacks during a
OL,8,Fwreath-laying ceremony, meeting first
OL,9,Fresponders and the families of victims.
OL,11,FThe King and Queen arrived by
OL,12,Fmotorcade and were greeted by
OL,13,Fdignitaries at the memorial.
OL,15,FThey were accompanied by former New
OL,16,FYork City Mayor Michael Bloomberg to
OL,17,Flay a bouquet of flowers at pools
OL,18,Fbearing the names of victims.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
