FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777529104
OL,3,CThe King and Queen visit 9/11 memorial
OL,4,Cas part of US state visit
OL,6,FThe Mayor of New York City, Zohran
OL,7,FMamdani, also attended the ceremony
OL,8,Fand shook hands with the King and
OL,9,FQueen.
OL,11,FEarlier in the day, Mamdani said he
OL,12,Fhoped to keep the event's focus on the
OL,13,Fvictims of the "horrific terror
OL,14,Fattacks" and not try to pursue any
OL,15,Fpolitical conversations.
OL,17,FAnthoula Katsimatides was among the
OL,18,FSept 11 victims' relatives who spoke
OL,19,Fwith the royal couple.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
