PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777529104
OL,3,CThe King and Queen visit 9/11 memorial
OL,4,Cas part of US state visit
OL,6,FHer brother, John Katsimatides, was a
OL,7,Fbroker for Cantor Fitzgerald and died
OL,8,Fat the World Trade Center.
OL,10,FThe King and Queen's visit to New York
OL,11,Fis the first trip by a reigning
OL,12,FBritish monarch since Queen Elizabeth
OL,13,FII visited in 2010.
OL,15,FThe King then visited an after-school,
OL,16,Furban farming effort that works with
OL,17,Fyoung people affected by food
OL,18,Finsecurity, before meeting with
OL,19,Ffinancial leaders in Manhattan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
