FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777529104
OL,3,CThe King and Queen visit 9/11 memorial
OL,4,Cas part of US state visit
OL,6,FThe Queen is also set to visit the New
OL,7,FYork Public Library, where she will
OL,8,Fadd to the library's famed collection
OL,9,Fof Winnie-the-Pooh stuffed animals in
OL,10,Fcelebration of the children's
OL,11,Fcharacter turns 100 this year.
OL,13,FThe couple are then set to attend a
OL,14,Freception for the King's Trust, a
OL,15,Fcharity Charles founded in 1976.
OL,17,FOn Monday, the King and Queen joined
OL,18,FPresident Donald Trump and first lady
OL,19,FMelania Trump for tea at the White
OL,20,FHouse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
