FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777529104
OL,3,CThe King and Queen visit 9/11 memorial
OL,4,Cas part of US state visit
OL,6,FThe next day, The King and Trump had a
OL,7,Fclosed-door meeting in the Oval Office.
OL,9,FThe King then delivered a rare speech
OL,10,Fbefore Congress (the first by a
OL,11,FBritish monarch since his late mother
OL,12,Fin 1991) followed by a formal state
OL,13,Fdinner at the White House.
OL,15,FThe monarchs are expected to make
OL,16,Fstops in Virginia before wrapping up
OL,17,Ftheir US visit back at the White House
OL,18,Fon Thursday with a formal farewell
OL,19,Ffrom Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
